<span class="line"><span class="token keyword">subgraph</span> displayFunc<span class="token text string">[&quot;&lt;code style=&quot;color:orange&quot;&gt;showWinner&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br/&gt;display func&quot;]</span></span>
